          </div>
          <div class='debug-info'>22222222-000 &rarr; 11111111-000</div>
          <div class='content markdown'><div class="assistant-text markdown"><p>Team test-coverage has one member still active. Shut down bob before retrying.</p>
  </div></div>
          
